Package org.gvsig.fmap.dal.coverage

Raster library API.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BufferFactory
    Factory for raster buffers
    RasterManager
    This class is responsible of the management of the library's business logic.
    RasterService
    Represents a Raster element.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RasterLibrary
    Library for API initialization and configuration.
    RasterLocator
    This locator is the entry point for the Raster library, providing access to all Raster services through the RasterManager .
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    RasterException
    Generic exception thrown in the Raster API when the exception or error may be dealt by the program or the user of the program which is a client of the Raster API.
    RasterMessageException
    Exception thrown when there is an error getting a Raster message.
